com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.domainrep.rdm.login

Interface LoginRefresh

  • All Superinterfaces:
    LoginMsg, MsgBase

    public interface LoginRefresh
extends LoginMsg
    The RDM Login Refresh. This message is used to respond to a Login Request message after the user's login is accepted.
    See Also:
    LoginMsg, LoginRefreshFlags
